name: Yeay Mao
shortLoreBlurb: Yeay Mao is a spirit/deity from Cambodia linked to sea guardian, vengeance. Offerings seek calm waters and life-giving rains.
overlapsLinks: Athena (Greek), Karttikeya (Hindu), Naga (India/SE Asia), Poseidon (Greek), Sekhmet (Egyptian), Tangaroa (Polynesia), Yemaya (Yoruba)
